snippet.title: MC STΔN  X @KSHMRmusic    HAATH VARTHI  (Official Video) | 2023
snippet.description:
“ HAATH VARTHI “ OUT NOW 🔥💯👇🏼 ( Official Music video ) ✅

STAN FAMILY 🙏🏻 Haq se love uh BHAILOG Bhot pyaarr Sabko
Kattar #fam Phele ki Public Abhi ki Public Sabku Salam bhaiiiiiiiiiii.............🙏🏼

10 Months Bad Gana Aaya 🥺  Baap re Full lambi Hogayeli Maam , i know Broskii Full Kantaal Aata Litreally Mein khud Mere Gaano Ka wait Karta 🥲 Kya bolu Maa ider Bhalta vishay chalu hai Samaj ke lo Baki kuch Nai Tracks on the way …… 🏃🏽

Line Se Appa vishay Khol 💯

Show sum love Gang !! Stay connected 🤝

Performed by: MC Stan, KSHMR
Lyrics: MC Stan
Produced by: KSHMR, Phenom 

Video Directed and Produced by Visuals by JD.

Haath Varthi Lyrics - 

Mere gaano pe haath varthi,
Agar nahi kiya yaha pe toh maar padhti,
Teri behen mujhse pyaar karti,
Mat maar usko uski nahi galti,
Sirf relate wo karti ,
P town bole toh yede log ki Bharti,
Mai gardish mai Bharti,
Aawaz thodi alag aari hogayeli sardi,
P Town se B Town tak apli chalti !!!

Tum gardi mai chalte toh dikhte nahi ,
Mai gardi mai chalta toh dikhta,
Tu dus time sochenga ,
aisa kyu likhta kyu ki mai sick tha ,
Ayee sickness bana mera dopeness. 
Skateboard Air 1 tight istari,
Kidd mai full homeless boneless staircase, 
Mujh pe kyu chodh dala beat ko ,
Maine chod dala beat ko,
Karu Kya disco MS Stan means, 
Toh darta nahi kisko aayi zavuntak Mitra mandal you know what I’m saying..

Kaisa hua meko pyaar, 
mera homie bola maar, 
Tune jhoot bola kyu ,
Maine diya tera saath!!! 

Mere gaano pe haath varthi ,
Agar nahi kiya yaha pe toh maar padhti,
Teri behen mujhse pyaar karti ,
Mat maar usko uski nahi galti,
Sirf relate wo karti ,
P town bole toh yede log ki Bharti ,
Mai gardish mai Bharti,
Aawaz thodi alag aari hogayeli sardi,
P Town se B Town tak apli chalti !!!

Mai ghusta jab club mai ,
basti ki public aayeli ,
matlab Confirm hai raade,
 It was my worst day  ,
Meri gang mei se koi toh bhi koyta nikale,
Public mai matter bada re ,
Shawty hot dikhri toh chadar failare ,
Yeh mere pe trapa bithare ,
Maa baap ko bolre haan Inlog ne maare,
Club mai teko entry nahi ,
Guest list mai naam tera maam hamne badach ka dale ,
Yeh Meko lagte bichare ,
Meri galti Kya inlog ke numbers nahi aare ,
Yeh Meko taadi pilare , yeh bache log Meko kyu taadi pilare ,
Daru mat paani pila re ,
Party mai entry hui toh shawty chupare.. !!

Mere gaano pe haath varthi ,
Agar nahi kiya yaha pe toh maar padhti,
Teri behen mujhse pyaar karti ,
Mat maar usko uski nahi galti,
Sirf relate wo karti ,
P town bole toh yede log ki Bharti, 
Mai gardish mai Bharti ,
Aawaz thodi alag aari hogayeli sardi ,
P Town se B Town tak apli chalti!!!

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 44 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 44 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 11th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma

Fazila Qazi as Aneela

नमस्ते दोस्तों!
AJIO Presents The Ranveer Show हिंदी के 161th Episode में आप सभी का स्वागत है. आज के Podcast में हमारे साथ जुड़ चुकी हैं Instagram Influencer Uorfi Javed जो अपने Fashion Sense और Social Media Presence के लिए जाना जाता है। वे Indian Television पर भी काम कर चुकी हैं। 

इस Podcast में हम बात करेंगे ढ़ेर सारी बातें Uorfi Javed की Early Life, Schooling, Teenage, Adulthood, Family, Father’s Brutal Behaviour, Mental Weakness, Mental Strength, Validation की ज़रूरत, Bachpan कैसे गया, Story Of Different Humans, Matriarchal Society, Patriarchal Society, Feminist Campaigns, What Is Feminism के बारे में। 
 
साथ ही साथ हम बात करेंगे Societal Balance, Male Dominant Society, Objectifying Women, Reason For Rapes, Homo Sapiens, Women Clothing, Freedom और GenZ की सोच के बारे में और भी ढ़ेर सारी बातें।

मैं आशा करता हूँ कि ये Video आप सभी Viewers को पसंद आएगा। खास तौर पर उन सभी को जिन्हें Bollywood और Social Media के किस्सों के बारे में जानने में Interest है। 

Uorfi Javed की Clothing Styles, Hollywood में Debut जैसी चीज़ों के बारे में हम Discuss करेंगे इस Hindi Podcast में सिर्फ और सिर्फ आपके Favourite BeerBiceps Hindi Channel Ranveer Allahbadia पर।

snippet.title: അന്നമ്മയുടെ നിങ്ങളറിയാത്ത  Motherhood Story | @SAMANWAYAMofficial | Josh Talks Malayalam
snippet.description:
ജീവിതം തോൽപിക്കാൻ നോക്കിയിട്ടും ഒന്നിലും തളരാതെ ജീവിതത്തിനോട്  പോലും വെല്ലുവിളിക്കുന്ന ഉഷ മാത്യു എന്ന അന്നമ്മ എല്ലാവർക്കും  ഒരു മാതൃകയാണ് . സംരംഭകയും, content creator -ഉമായ അന്നമ്മ, ജീവിതത്തിൽ  ഒത്തിരി പ്രശ്ങ്ങൾ നേരിട്ടിട്ടും, വീട്ടുകാരും കൂട്ടുകാരും കൈവിട്ടിട്ടും തളരാതെ മുന്നോട്ടു പോയി. ഇന്നത്തെ Josh Talksൽ തന്റെ ഗർഭകാല സമയങ്ങളിൽ അനുഭവിച്ച വെല്ലുവിളികളും അതെങ്ങനെ അതിജീവിച്ചെന്ന കരളലിയിക്കുന്ന യാഥാർഥ്യമാണ് നമ്മോടു പങ്കുവെക്കുന്നത്.

 ഒന്നിലധികം ഗർഭം അലസലുകളും, ശൈശവാവസ്ഥയിൽ 10 കുട്ടികളും നഷ്ടപ്പെട്ടിട്ടും, അമ്മയാകാനുള്ള അന്നമ്മയുടെ വാശി  ഉപേക്ഷിക്കാൻ തയ്യാറായില്ല. ഡോക്ടർമാരും മറ്റുള്ളവരും അവളുടെ ശ്രമം നിർത്താൻ പറഞ്ഞിട്ടും അവൾ സ്വയം സഹിച്ചു പോരാടി. അന്നമ്മയുടെ കഥ മനുഷ്യാത്മാവിന്റെ ശക്തിയുടെയും പ്രതിരോധത്തിന്റെയും ശക്തമായ ഓർമ്മപ്പെടുത്തലാണ്. നമ്മൾ നേരിടുന്ന വെല്ലുവിളികൾ എത്ര ഭയാനകമായാലും നമ്മുടെ സ്വപ്നങ്ങൾ ഒരിക്കലും കൈവിടാതിരിക്കേണ്ടതിന്റെ പ്രാധാന്യം  മനസിലാക്കാൻ ഈ കഥ നിങ്ങളെ സഹായിക്കും.

Usha Mathew is a role model for everyone who defies even life and never gets tired of anything. An entrepreneur and content creator, Annamma faced many problems in her life and continued to move forward without giving up, despite being abandoned by her family and friends. In today's josh talks, Annamma shares her experiences of overcoming personal challenges. 

Despite multiple miscarriages and the loss of 12 of her children in infancy, Annamma refused to give up her desire to be a mother. Despite doctors and others telling her to stop trying, she fought and persevered. Annamma's story is a powerful reminder of the strength and resilience of the human spirit, and this story will help you understand the importance of never giving up on our dreams, no matter how daunting the challenges we face.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com  ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.
If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalees. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ അവർ നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.

#joshtalksmalayalam #motivation  #nevergiveup

 ഒന്നിലധികം ഗർഭം അലസലുകളും, ശൈശവാവസ്ഥയിൽ 10 കുട്ടികളും നഷ്ടപ്പെട്ടിട്ടും, അമ്മയാകാനുള്ള അന്നമ്മയുടെ വാശി  ഉപേക്ഷിക്കാൻ തയ്യാറായില്ല. ഡോക്ടർമാരും മറ്റുള്ളവരും അവളുടെ ശ്രമം നിർത്താൻ പറഞ്ഞിട്ടും അവൾ സ്വയം സഹിച്ചു പോരാടി. അന്നമ്മയുടെ കഥ മനുഷ്യാത്മാവിന്റെ ശക്തിയുടെയും പ്രതിരോധത്തിന്റെയും ശക്തമായ ഓർമ്മപ്പെടുത്തലാണ്. നമ്മൾ നേരിടുന്ന വെല്ലുവിളികൾ എത്ര ഭയാനകമായാലും നമ്മുടെ സ്വപ്നങ്ങൾ ഒരിക്കലും കൈവിടാതിരിക്കേണ്ടതിന്റെ പ്രാധാന്യം  മനസിലാക്കാൻ ഈ കഥ നിങ്ങളെ സഹായിക്കും.

Usha Mathew is a role model for everyone who defies even life and never gets tired of anything. An entrepreneur and content creator, Annamma faced many problems in her life and continued to move forward without giving up, despite being abandoned by her family and friends. In today's josh talks, Annamma shares her experiences of overcoming personal challenges. 

Despite multiple miscarriages and the loss of 12 of her children in infancy, Annamma refused to give up her desire to be a mother. Despite doctors and others telling her to stop trying, she fought and persevered. Annamma's story is a powerful reminder of the strength and resilience of the human spirit, and this story will help you understand the importance of never giving up on our dreams, no matter how daunting the challenges we face.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com  ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.
If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalees. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ അവർ നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 43 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 10th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Tere Bin Episode 43 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 10th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3767 - Bhide To Leave Gokuldham?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3769 - 12 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3769: Bhide Ki Asli Baat
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha decides to find out the truth after becoming dubious of Bhide's news. As a result, Jetha asks Taarak for assistance, and the two of them come up with an idea to get Bhide to break the real news. Bhide, meantime, expresses to Madhavi his relief at the realization that Tapu and Sonu are only close friends. Bhide is startled to see Jetha and Taarak when the doorbell rings. Jetha presents himself to Bhide as though he is aware of the facts surrounding the exciting news and that Bhide has been lying about Popatlal's engagement. Will Jetha and Taarak be able to persuade Bhide to be truthful?
 
Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3769, 12 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3768 - 11 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3768: Bhide Ko Laga Jhatka
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha is waiting for Bhide and Madhavi to tell him about their intriguing news when they arrive at Gada's house, but the entire Gokhuldham community is already there. Bhide wants to speak with Jetha in private, but when Sonu and Tapu show up there, they share some wonderful news about winning a poetry contest. Later, Tapu thanks Champaklal for all of his love and support by giving him the rose and the card. Madhavi and Bhide are taken aback by Tapu's behavior. To find out what happens after that, watch the episode!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3768, 11 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Modern Love Chennai - Official Trailer | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video Presents
Modern Love Chennai - Official Trailer
Directed by: Bharathiraja, Balaji Sakthivel, Thiagarajan Kumararaja, Rajumurugan, Krishnakumar Ramakumar, Akshay Sundher
Starring: Ritu Varma, Ashok Selvan, Ramya Nambessan, Wamiqa, Sri Gouri Priya, Samyuktha Vishwanathan, Pawan Alex, Aniiruth Kanakarajan, T J Bhanu, Sanjula Sarathi, Chu Khoy Sheng,
Srikrishna Dayal, Vasudevan Murali, Vasundhara, Kishore, Vijayalakshmi, PB
Producer: Tyler Durden and Kino Fist
Music Directors: Isaignani Ilaiyaraaja, Yuvan Shankar Raja, G.V. Prakash Kumar, Sean Roldan
Writers: Balaji Tharaneetharan, Rajumurugan, Reshma Ghatala, Pratheep Kumar S, Thiagarajan Kumararaja
Music Label: Sony Music Entertainment India Pvt. Ltd.

Official Release Date: May 18, 2023 only on Prime Video

About:
Love exists in so many different dimensions that it is hard to define, yet easy to ‘know’.
Modern Love Chennai is an eclectic bouquet of love stories – funny, quirky, deep and puzzling. 
While the stories converse with your heart, you also catch a glimpse into the soul of Chennai and its unique terrains and diverse inhabitants. 
 
Modern Love Chennai is inspired by articles published in the New York Times and has been adapted for the Tamil landscape. 

For more such videos, subscribe to our YouTube channel ► https://amzn.to/Subscribe
Don't forget to push the Bell 🔔 icon to never miss an update.

For more updates, stay connected with us on
► Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PrimeVideoIN/
► Twitter: https://twitter.com/PrimeVideoIN
► Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/primevideoin
► Watch Now: https://primevideo.com

About Prime Video
Prime Video is a premium streaming service that offers Prime members a collection of award-winning Amazon Original series, thousands of movies and TV shows—all with the ease of finding what they love to watch in one place.  Find out more at PrimeVideo.com.

Included with Prime Video: 
Thousands of acclaimed TV shows and movies across languages and geographies, including Indian films such as Jai Bhim, Shershaah, Toofaan, Sardar Udham, Coolie No. 1, Gulabo Sitabo, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Durgamati, Chhalaang, Hello Charlie, Cold Case, Narappa, Sara’s, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi and Tuck Jagadish, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Mumbai Diaries 26/11, The Last Hour, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Breathe, Comicstaan Semma Comedy Pa, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Inside Edge and Made In Heaven. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like The Tomorrow War, Coming 2 America, Cinderella, Borat Subsequent Moviefilm, Without Remorse, The Wheel of Time, American Gods, One Night in Miami, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Cruel Summer, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel and many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi and Bengali.

Instant Access: 
Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV and multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid and post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices and tablets and watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.

Enhanced experiences
Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- and High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies and TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing.

Included with Prime
Prime Video is available in India at no extra cost with Prime membership for just ₹1499 annually or ₹179 monthly. New customers can find out more at www.amazon.in/prime and subscribe to a free 30-day trial.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3770 - 13 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3770: Popatlal Ki Shaadi Ki Charcha
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak and Anjali talk about Popatlal's wedding and feel bad for him. Anjali tells Taarak that she has asked all her relatives and friends to find a girl for Popatlal. Anjali tells Taarak that he has laced a sweet dish for Taarak in his lunch box today, but Taarak asks for a kiss from Anjali. She gives her a flying kiss in the compound but realizes that Bapuji has seen her giving a kiss to Taarak. Later, the Tapu Sena tells Bapuji about their new games and rhymes. Watch the full episode to know more.

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

►*About*
-------------

RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

Bhakt Banerjee is not angry - he's distraught and disappointed in the people of Karnataka ... despite being warned that the state was going in the direction of Kerala - people did not listen and were more worried about small issues like corruption and in inflation. HOW CAN THEY BE SO BLIND??? 

They refused to vote for the Supreme Leader despite his personal appeal ....despite his road show....despite what he's done for the state!!! - PAPA maaf nahi karenge !!!

snippet.title: "Let It Go" | Fotty Seven | Official Music Video
snippet.description:
'Let It Go' is a song with different meanings. You decide what it means to you. 

Written, performed and recorded by Fotty Seven
Beat produced by SiddyBoy
Mixed and mastered by Benny Steele

Follow me on Instagram:

https://www.instagram.com/fottyseven

Lyrics:

Koi Pyar wala scene nahi
Kisi aur pe yakeen nahi 
Apni soch ko mai sunn-na nahi chahta
Dekhta hoon videos, aati jab tak neend nahi


Teri yaad daude naso mei 
Teri yaad kare suffocate
Log zindagi udate hai kasho mei 
But I’m proud of myself kabhi pada nahi nasho mei 

Mujhe hi pata hai kaise deal kar raha hoon 
Lagta nahi bilkul bhi heal kar raha hoon
Mere pas bas meri ma hai, usse kya hi batau kya mai feel kar raha hoon

Wo nahi samjhegi, kasam degi apni, ruth te hue 
Kehti tu hai mera superstar 
Kaise dekhu tujhko mai toot te hue 

Mai ek ladka hoon
Aata hai achhe se dard chhupana 
Chhoda agar maine dard chhupana 
Ye band kar denge mujhe mard bulana 

Aajkal baitha rehta hoon mai gym mei 
Aajkal dekhta nahi hoon mai filmei 
Aajkal dikhta nahi hoon mehfil mei
Aajkal koi bhi nahi hai mere dil mei

Malum hi nahi malum hi nahi 
Chal Kya raha hai mujhe malum hi nahi 
Kar kya raha hoon mujhe malum hi nahi
Ab wo haath ferti hai mere baalo mei nahi

Shayad hi kabhi hamari baat hoti hai 
Log dekhe mujhe jab bhi teri baat hoti hai 
Teri yaad sabse zyada aaye tab 
Jab bhi tu kabhi mere saath hoti hai 

And it’s ok
And it’s alright 
Likh denge gaano mei jo hum kabhi na bol paye 
Aankhei phone par shayad tera call aaye 
Raaz khul gaye lekin dil kabhi na khol paye 

Baatei dil ke kone mei aaj
Jo mai sunn leta tha tere bole bina
Yun toh milta hoon roz tujhe sone ke baad
Lekin achhe milunga theek hone ke baad

Subscribe for more.
tags: mere pas bas meri ma hai

snippet.title: Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 683 & 684 | Recap
snippet.description:
Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 683 & 684 | Recap

While Naaz forces Rupi to give her share of his land, Nehmat steps in and desires to obtain her share as well. However, Ekam expresses his displeasure with Nehmat and rebukes her for her changed demeanour. How will Nehmat manage the situation?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

snippet.description:
Today in our village, we make our village traditional sarbath juice with farm-fresh King Coconut! Tender Coconut water is most effective in summer season. King Coconut variant is a very rare variant than a normal coconut!

We add basil seeds and King coconut meat to make this juice as healthy drink! The taste is divine!

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3768 - Bhide Ko Karni Hai Zaroori Baat?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi

snippet.description:

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.description:
Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 682 & 683 | Recap

Nehmat gets intoxicated and decides to expose Jasmine's truth in front of everyone. Jasmine feels apprehensive about Nehmat's decision and intends to prevent her from disclosing the truth. Will Jasmine be able to stop her before it's too late?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

About MalaimurasuNews TV

Malaimurasu TV (Tamil: மாலைமுரசு ) is a 24x7 live news channel in Tamil launched on Jun 09, 2016. Due to its independent editorial stance it became extremely popular in India and abroad within days of its launch and continues to remain so till date.The channel looks at issues through the eyes of the common man and serves as a platform that airs people's views.The editorial policy is built on strong ethics and fair reporting methods that does not favour or oppose any individual, ideology, group, government, organisation or sponsor.The channel’s primary aim is taking unbiased and accurate information to the socially conscious common man.
Besides giving live and current information the channel broadcasts news on sports,  business and international affairs. It also offers a wide array of week end programmes.
The company also publishes popular Malaimurasu Newspaper & Tamil magazines - Kanmani and Ponmani.
